author: mmusich
body:
#### PR description:

Title says it all, the BeamSpot Payload Inspector is expanded in order to be able to display also objects of the type `BeamSpotOnlineObjects` as introduced in PR https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/29662

#### PR validation:

Relies on existing unit tests, plus the added one in this PR.
Example of output from the unit test:

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5082376/87219959-0f592a80-c360-11ea-9f84-13c9157c1f93.png)


#### if this PR is a backport please specify the original PR and why you need to backport that PR:

This PR is not a backport, no backport is needed.
title: Expand BeamSpot Payload Inspector to account for new BeamSpotOnline Object
